220
00:10:02,841 --> 00:10:03,384
va

221
00:10:04,548 --> 00:10:05,456
permettre

222
00:10:06,114 --> 00:10:08,485
une transformation
des habitudes et des routines,

223
00:10:08,485 --> 00:10:11,436
